<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Fiche d'Inscription</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
        <h1 style="color: #2c3e50; border-bottom: 2px solid #3498db; padding-bottom: 10px;">Fiche d'Inscription</h1>
    </div>

    <div style="background-color: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 5px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #2980b9; margin-top: 0;">Informations Personnelles</h2>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong style="color: #2c3e50;">Nom:</strong> <span style="color: #333;">{{ candidate.name }}</span></p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong style="color: #2c3e50;">Sexe:</strong> <span style="color: #333;">{{ candidate.sexe }}</span></p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong style="color: #2c3e50;">Date de Naissance:</strong> <span style="color: #333;">{{ candidate.dateOfBirth|date('d/m/Y') }}</span></p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong style="color: #2c3e50;">Lieu de Naissance:</strong> <span style="color: #333;">{{ candidate.placeOfBirth }}</span></p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong style="color: #2c3e50;">Nationalité:</strong> <span style="color: #333;">{{ candidate.nationality }}</span></p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong style="color: #2c3e50;">CNI:</strong> <span style="color: #333;">{{ candidate.cni }}</span></p>
    </div>

    <div style="background-color: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 5px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #2980b9; margin-top: 0;">Coordonnées</h2>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong style="color: #2c3e50;">Téléphone:</strong> <span style="color: #333;">{{ candidate.phoneNumber }}</span></p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong style="color: #2c3e50;">Email:</strong> <span style="color: #333;">{{ candidate.email }}</span></p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong style="color: #2c3e50;">Région:</strong> <span style="color: #333;">{{ candidate.region }}</span></p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong style="color: #2c3e50;">Département:</strong> <span style="color: #333;">{{ candidate.depertement }}</span></p>
    </div>

    <div style="background-color: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 5px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #2980b9; margin-top: 0;">Informations Académiques</h2>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong style="color: #2c3e50;">Domaine:</strong> <span style="color: #333;">{{ candidate.field }}</span></p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong style="color: #2c3e50;">Centre d'Examen:</strong> <span style="color: #333;">{{ candidate.examinationCenter }}</span></p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong style="color: #2c3e50;">Certificat:</strong> <span style="color: #333;">{{ candidate.certificate }}</span></p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong style="color: #2c3e50;">Année du Certificat:</strong> <span style="color: #333;">{{ candidate.certificateYear }}</span></p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong style="color: #2c3e50;">Langue:</strong> <span style="color: #333;">{{ candidate.language }}</span></p>
    </div>

    <div style="background-color: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 5px; padding: 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #2980b9; margin-top: 0;">Informations de Paiement</h2>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong style="color: #2c3e50;">Numéro de Transaction:</strong> <span style="color: #333;">{{ candidate.transactionNumber }}</span></p>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; font-size: 12px; color: #7f8c8d;">
        <p>Ce document est généré automatiquement. Veuillez ne pas le modifier.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>